{"tid":1501380,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[避難處]今晚 (24/8) 於九龍灣國際展貿中心舉辦的HANA菊梓喬演唱會將會如期舉行","createTime":"2019-08-24T10:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T14:30:43.000Z","uid":66260,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3c51154948c3a185805e636ab6fdb0eaafb58d2c","tid":1501380,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:47:56.000Z","msg":"星夢娛樂集團 The Voice Entertainment Group<br />\n3小時 &middot; <br />\n主辦單位服務啟示<br />\n<br />\n今晚 (24/8) 於九龍灣國際展貿中心舉辦的「HANA菊梓喬只想與你在一起演唱會」將會如期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n鑒於九龍灣附近路面情況有可能出現擠塞，主辦單位星夢娛樂集團及理想天映傳媒有限公司於完場後將會為觀眾提供旅遊巴服務，接載大家離開。所有觀眾可憑演唱會門票票尾乘坐旅遊巴至佐敦逸東酒店旁 (鄰近佐敦地鐵站)。"},{"pid":"00fb5644f4a463d12ca2e1896907a20975ade098","tid":1501380,"uid":112316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"多齒症"},{"pid":"bd96dbd87deeb69bec1472d38e96a76b7de46528","tid":1501380,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d8259ca2d1db91d43e2c7f3477dfe8c95731266","tid":1501380,"uid":34334,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:49:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b95e71b82ff68183dfc029b649173e8a5cffea69","tid":1501380,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381fdb300f215a67d0bb993a5caada3371d8675f","tid":1501380,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:51:51.000Z","msg":"仲有人夠膽去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63618aad79e3109ee8d7ea32e8b49fdac50bd2bb","tid":1501380,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"381fdb300f215a67d0bb993a5caada3371d8675f","tid":1501380,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:51:51.000Z","msg":"仲有人夠膽去？<img 